data.description: Welcome to Lakeview Commons!  This townhouse is one of the largest floor plans available in the neighborhood including 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms with a large loft.  The primary suite is located downstairs with a walk-in closet and a bathroom featuring dual sinks and a garden tub/shower combination.  The kitchen has plenty of cabinet space and all appliances are included. There is also a powder room, laundry room and living space downstairs.  Upstairs you will notice a large loft that can be used as a flex space/media room.  The additional 3 bedrooms are all spacious with great sized closets. The backyard opens up to a pond that is stocked with fish for those that love the outdoors and fishing. The monthly HOA covers exterior building maintenance & exterior insurance, termitebond, access to the pool, and lawn maintenance.  There is also a neighborhood park.  There is a one-car garage and one assigned parking space. Also makes a great investment property/rental!
